(@ID + 2, "You are too late! The Hunger Games are in progress!"),
(@ID + 3, "You are too late! There's no more room for new participants!"),
(@ID + 4, "You want to participate in the Hunger Games?\n<Khat'nis chuckles.>\nYou are too weak. You lack the experience for that. Only the mightiest and the most experienced champions are able to participate... And you are not one of them.");
